thread.title: LeBron James Can’t Do It by Himself (Or Can He?)

author: Jason Gay
title: LeBron James Can’t Do It by Himself (Or Can He?)
text:
Boston
The game was, well, a stinker. Even when it was close, it was cloddish, not even in the realm of mediocre, much less a masterpiece. The Boston Celtics hit just 34% of their shots. The box says Cleveland hit 45%, but that number sounds charitable. Don’t let anyone glam up the retelling of Game 7 of the 2018 NBA Eastern Conference Finals: no one is sending the highlights to the Hall of Fame.
Except...
